<p rend="centre"> Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa</p>

<p rend="book">Sūrassatīnīti</p>

<p rend="subhead">Paṭhamo bhāgo</p>

<p rend="chapter">Paṇāmagāthā</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="1"><hi rend="paranum">1</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Mukhamhā <pb ed="M" n="1.0001" /> bhagavantassa,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Sugandhakamalā subhā;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Sañjātaṃ uttamaṃ vāṇiṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Vandāmi vittamānasā.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="2"><hi rend="paranum">2</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Samajjhiṭṭho racissāmi,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Dakkhena rājamantinā;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Nāmena santena,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Nītiṃ lokahitāvahaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Sālaṅkāraṃ sopadesaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Nāmenāhaṃ svarassatiṃ.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="3"><hi rend="paranum">3</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Pekkhantvimaṃ nītiṃ santā,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Mañjūsarukkhasannibhaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Nānopadesasaṃpuṇṇaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Sadatthakusalā sadā.</p>
</body>
